  "detailed_description": "<i>Your friend went missing, and a dark force is looming in this already deranged world. You, Sheriff Toadster, are the only toad that can save him in this intense action side-scroller adventure! Jump around, shoot your way through and investigate the mysterious disappearance, all while exploring the land and meeting the intriguing characters of this universe!</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/b4bbe85cafe8c2a40c9deddc3c013df8.avif?t=1748894741\" width=600 height=68 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/27d1f3ac14e60d019b3e4a5db0b15873.poster.avif?t=1748894741\" width=542 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/27d1f3ac14e60d019b3e4a5db0b15873.webm?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/27d1f3ac14e60d019b3e4a5db0b15873.mp4?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Avoid traps and dangers, move around the enviroment with precise moves to get through all the obstacles along your way!<br></li><li> Dash around, climb walls and jump around to get through all the challenges this world has to offer!<br></li><li> Roam around beaches, forests, secret factories and more to find your friend.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/54a18a3c743d6e4dbccd989705857153.avif?t=1748894741\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/dc59fc38ba5d307eb7750ee405321709.poster.avif?t=1748894741\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/dc59fc38ba5d307eb7750ee405321709.webm?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/dc59fc38ba5d307eb7750ee405321709.mp4?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Defeat the enemies that will come along your way!<br></li><li> Use multiple weapons and special abilities to approach encounters with the most optimal strategy.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/8ec211411674cf59cd7010ab760b7120.webp?t=1748894741\" width=600 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/12dd0590265a83262a5da4c254afbf55.poster.avif?t=1748894741\" width=542 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/12dd0590265a83262a5da4c254afbf55.webm?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/12dd0590265a83262a5da4c254afbf55.mp4?t=1748894741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Your old friends have been corrupted and want to defeat you!<br></li><li> Challenge them in epic boss fights to rid them of their sickness!<br></li><li> And maybe make up with them later?</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113680/extras/d82bbe7d0159775dcb88a0a8528fd00a.webp?t=1748894741\" width=600 height=61 /></span>",
